// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3544 — Mass File Rename (stormous)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: b4999496-5bf5-5774-aa95-076625869ad3

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
